         "nvidia-dkms · nvidia-utils · lib32-nvidia-utils\nWorks with all kernels including linux-zen"),
        ("amd",     "AMD / ATI (Open-Source)",
         "mesa · vulkan-radeon · libva-mesa-driver · lib32-mesa\nRecommended for all AMD / Radeon GPUs"),
        ("intel",   "Intel (Open-Source)",
         "mesa · vulkan-intel · intel-media-driver · lib32-mesa\nFor integrated Intel graphics (HD, Iris, Arc)"),
        ("default", "Generic / Open-Source (mesa only)",
         "mesa\nSafe fallback for unknown or unsupported hardware"),
    ]

